        "process.title": "Proprietary Process & The Portal",
        "process.subtitle": "Forget chaotic email threads. With us, the entire process—from concept to launch—is seamlessly tracked in your dedicated Client Portal, ensuring 100% transparency and premier collaboration.",
        "process.step1.title": "Audit & Onboarding",
        "process.step1.desc": "We start with a strategy session. You receive secure access to The Portal, housing your project roadmap, timeline, and all crucial assets.",
