        // FAQ
        "faq.label": "FAQ",
        "faq.title": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "faq.subtitle": "Answers to the most common questions",
        "faq.q1": "How long does a typical project take?",
        "faq.a1": "Project duration depends on complexity. A website takes 2–4 weeks, an e-commerce store 4–6 weeks, and a mobile app 8–12 weeks. Every project starts with a detailed analysis and timeline.",
        "faq.q2": "How much does AI agent implementation cost?",
        "faq.a2": "AI implementation costs depend on the scope of automation. A basic AI agent starts from 1,000 EUR, and an advanced system with integrations from 3,000 EUR. We offer free consultations to estimate costs.",
        "faq.q3": "Do you offer post-launch support?",
        "faq.a3": "Yes! Every project includes 30 days of warranty support. We also offer monthly support packages covering updates, monitoring, and optimization.",
        "faq.q4": "What technologies do you use?",
        "faq.a4": "We work with cutting-edge technologies: Next.js, React, React Native, Google Gemini AI, N8N, Shopify, Wix, Firebase, AWS, and many more. We select the tech stack based on project needs.",
