        "faq.sectionTitle": "Myths & Facts",
        "faq.sectionSubtitle": "Answers to frequently asked questions from leaders entering the digital transformation in 2026.",
        "faq.q6": "Myth: AI implementation will replace my team. Fact: AI is an assistant, not a replacement.",
        "faq.a6": "Many entrepreneurs fear AI will eliminate jobs. In reality, our AI Agents automate 60-80% of the most repetitive tasks, freeing your team for strategic goals.",
        "faq.q7": "Myth: Advanced AI technology is only for large corporations. Fact: SMEs benefit the most.",
        "faq.a7": "That's not true. Agencies like ECM Digital design automation solutions based on n8n and cheaper AI models so agile SMEs can achieve powerful results in the first weeks.",
