        "faq.a8": "A standard website takes about 2-4 weeks. A complex platform takes 6-10 weeks, focusing on performance and unique UI/UX.",
        "faq.q9": "Do you provide ongoing maintenance and support after completion?",
        "faq.a9": "Absolutely! We provide full post-deployment support, monitoring stability and infrastructure security.",
        "faq.q10": "How can I estimate automation or MVP development costs?",
        "faq.a10": "Every idea goes through a free consultation phase. Thanks to advanced code generation tools, we build much cheaper than traditional estimates.",
